Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.63,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.51,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.01,0:00:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.19,0:00:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.84,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.12,0:00:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.22,0:01:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.70,0:01:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.73,0:01:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.52,0:01:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为得了严重的感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫回到了现代来养病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.53,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多同学都到家里来看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我突然发现\N第二天就要考试了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学  求求你\N帮我恶补吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.78,0:01:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么\N烧一直都没有退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我觉得快完蛋的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喝下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏有那帖犬夜叉妈妈\N传给他的秘方草药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算可以到学校参加考试了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.26,0:02:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第90话 草太大胆的爱情告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气好  心情也特别好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上\N身体已经好得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试也应付过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次多亏有犬夜叉你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你喔  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…别再说这些了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间在那边说客套话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.63,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如早点跟我回去算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我去逛街好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.31,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得要\N陪你做这些事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要出远门了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好准备点东西\N怎么可以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N上一次你不是才跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不准我出门吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次是上次  这次是这次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么跟什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像这样一起走在街上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.58,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  这些是不是吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.29,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我们先买什么好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.89,0:03:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买忍者食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杯面应该在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇塞  好多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要买哪一种呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样问我我怎么知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会买太多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛突然停住不走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  为什么要躲起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买送人当礼物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道买哪种好对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决…决定以后你再告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子到底在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说了是真的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把脚伸进脸盆的时候\N不小心摔进浴缸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸好可怜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛\N说到底还是他自己太不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有受伤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上肿了好大一个包呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  好惨哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.98,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有食欲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这种时候\N我看只有用这个秘方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们日暮神社\N代代相传的人鱼鳞片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个鳞片\N贴在肚脐上睡一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很神奇的什么事都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蚋来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吃掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来\N我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太这孩子到底怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是什么地方不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病分很多种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种叫作恋爱病听过没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱病…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N我晚上得煮个红豆饭来庆祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就用恋爱病\N当作戈薇的请假理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我用这种理由也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理由一定骗得了人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信啊  爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.49,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凄美的病啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我想要跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.17,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们男人之间的重要秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没事的话我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你先别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  有什么事情快点说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是恋爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是不是就是永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛无缘无故问这种问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你喔  你跟姐姐两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底先谁开口说喜欢对方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  到底是谁嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然问这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们两个人在交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不是情侣的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐怎么会常常特地\N向学校请假去找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐生病了\N你也不会大老远来看她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我  到底谁先开口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么告白的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.13,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候\N跟戈薇说过这些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是\N是姐姐先开口咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐说了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说姐姐跟你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在\N你们都还没有向对方表示过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还没有表示过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做就怎么做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的这个女生\N她叫做小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没听你提过耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳是我们班上的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.57,0:09:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课的时候就坐在我旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心目中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳这个女生真的好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛水汪汪的皮肤又白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从国外回来\N她不喜欢吃芹菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连书包也不是普通的书包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我对你说的东西\N不太了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之\N你爱上她了  对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.11,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不知道\N小瞳是怎么看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.11,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定去跟小瞳好好地告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种事要来问我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以陪我练习一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说希望你可以\N陪我练习怎么向她表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能就一次哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  快开始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有做好心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不开始我可要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.35,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…两个在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么好笑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是笑你干嘛做这种傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一开始\N直接来问我不是比较好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的心理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再怎么说呢\N也比犬夜叉清楚得很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是女人当然比我懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.89,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事情包在我的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我可爱的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么样都会想出办法来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够帅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一身打扮\N我相信一定可以搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.18,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记着  午休的时候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都先别透露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到放学再把小瞳叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个可以单独相处的地方\N跟她说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.49,0:12:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道\N要我整天穿这身衣服上课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.92,0:12:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你就要忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.76,0:12:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是你的人生大事对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.93,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  祝你好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日暮草太  万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  我们一起欢呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.77,0:12:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说示爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  示爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇\N北条同学真的向你示爱了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你会兴奋成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这就是叫劈腿了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搞错了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是北条同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你还没有跟那个\N凶神恶煞的男朋友说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情\N如果不妥善处理的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会给自己惹了一身麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是你们想的这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是我自己\N我说的是草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是你弟弟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是说他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天\N他要在学校向同学表白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得怎么样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你这么兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的事  怪不得这么开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你平时绝对不会这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了草太还没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他被甩了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也很难说\N搞不好真的是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是你设计得不够好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.23,0:13:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草…草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副愁眉苦脸的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.38,0:14:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看八九不离十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.61,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定吃了闭门羹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么无精打采的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  别愁眉苦脸的行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人到处都是\N根本不用怕找不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有被甩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是  那为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不出口?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我照姐姐说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学以后\N约了小瞳到操场那边见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  草太同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有什么事我要回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  等一下  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌吞吞吐吐\N没有男子气概的男生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我就说不出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就这么结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本什么\N都还没有跟人家说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怕什么哭什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会被人家甩掉\N也是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不强壮  又不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连话都说不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这样说自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己不好\N改变一下不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:15:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上\N让你变成真正的男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.67,0:16:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.23,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  不是做得还不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪\N等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.25,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪\N你教草太耍拳是想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在帮他建立信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要信心建立起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么都没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦  不是在说你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.07,0:16:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我太敏感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过刚刚的特训\N你是不是变得比较厉害了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我看哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你比刚刚强太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟刚刚比起来\N简直变成另外一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续练下去  草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连爷爷跟妈妈都出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  草太要继续努力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.07,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像被耍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教草太简直比打妖怪还要累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果顺利的话一切都值得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子还真是胆子小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.22,0:17:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个弟弟还真是没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点小事都不能下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢人家就\N干脆一点跟人家说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是对自己信心不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.71,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要打退堂鼓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.75,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己想了想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次训练\N怎么能让我变得更坚强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的个性\N没那么容易改过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿…穿帮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你给我振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老是三心二意犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉大丈夫应该下定决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这样说我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那边咯哩罗唆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  我不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我听清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.52,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有跟小瞳说清楚之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你回家来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.78,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不跟她说清楚\N就回家的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别想走进这个大门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里明明是我的家耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就叫做气魄  气魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你下定决心去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么都没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子还真是不干脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.03,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你\N你到底是不是喜欢人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个男人对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就鼓起勇气\N一股作气跟对方说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个做姐姐的\N当然要去支持弟弟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.83,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.83,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天好像心事重重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一件\N很重要的事要告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.83,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男人对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.11,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就要鼓起勇气\N一股作气跟对方说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.11,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会觉得我很没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连话也说不清楚\N又不能保护女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很喜欢你  小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意做我的女朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.88,0:20:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才上小学三年级耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很厉害嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有忘了什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧  我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了  草太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就上路吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.49,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.73,0:22:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.01,0:22:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.76,0:22:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.27,0:22:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.04,0:23:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.28,0:23:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.79,0:23:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.56,0:23:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.03,0:23:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.55,0:23:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛  你在找什么啊七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.09,0:23:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找\N小梅村子里那只小花啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.59,0:23:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从一个奇怪的巫师说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.39,0:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会给村民带来灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.63,0:23:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花就被赶出村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.60,0:23:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花不但聪明\N而且长很像云母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.10,0:24:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫是老鼠的天敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.30,0:24:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次村子里\N突然被大批的老鼠袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.34,0:24:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定有什么关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.11,0:24:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉\N怪异的巫师和黑色云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就交给我来应付吧



